        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">The provided European production volume is an estimated value as described below. 
The global demand of sodium cyanide amounted to 1305.3 kt in 2023, based on: Expert Market Research (&lt;https://www.expertmarketresearch.com/&gt;), available here: &lt;https://www.globenewswire.com/en/news-release/2023/06/20/2691437/0/en/Sodium-Cyanide-Market-Size-Share-Analysis-Growth-Trends-Forecasts-2023-2028.html&gt;, last accessed 23-09-2023.
The European counterpart is estimated to be 110'504'024 kg, considering the nominal GDP of EU in 2022, equal to 14'040'893'546'587 US$ and in the World, equal to 100'562'011'134'034 US$, available here: &lt;https://api.worldbank.org/v2/en/indicator/NY.GDP.MKTP.CD?downloadformat=excel&gt; , last accessed 23-09.2023.


</productionVolumeComment>
